Mark-Paul Gosselaar https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark-Paul_Gosselaar 0 Mark-Paul Harry Gosselaar (; born March 1, 1974) is an American actor. He is known for his television roles as Zack Morris in Saved by the Bell, Detective John Clark in NYPD Blue, and Peter Bash in Franklin Bash. He was the lead in the 1998 film Dead Man on Campus, and starred in the 2016 TV series Pitch. Mark-Paul_Harry_Gosselaar ( ; born March_1_,_1974 ) is an_American_actor .
